OL,3,CWarm hub supports people through cold
OL,4,Csnap health warning
OL,6,FA Scottish Borders warm bank - in the
OL,7,Fmidst of a cold snap weather warning -
OL,8,Fcontinues to support locals despite
OL,9,Ftheir financial struggles.
OL,11,FA warm hub at the Royal British Legion
OL,12,Fclub, in Coldstream, was one of more
OL,13,Fthan 200 initiatives across Scotland
OL,14,Fto support people when the cost-of-
OL,15,Fliving crisis struck two years ago.
OL,17,FThis week the UK Health Security
OL,18,FAgency issued the first amber cold
OL,19,Fweather alert of this winter season -
OL,20,Fwarning older people and those with
OL,21,Fsignificant health conditions.
