OL,3,CWarm hub supports people through cold
OL,4,Csnap health warning
OL,6,FThe warn bank has been encouraging
OL,7,Fpeople to use their service amid the
OL,8,Fcold snap warning.
OL,10,FRussell Kirk, organiser of the warm
OL,11,Fspace in Coldstream, says their
OL,12,Fservice is there to help people get
OL,13,Fthrough the coldest times of the
OL,14,Fwinter months.
OL,16,FHe said: "People are invited to come
OL,17,Fin, spend a few hours with us and get
OL,18,Fa warm bowl of soup - there's a lot of
OL,19,Fsocial company as well.
