OL,3,CWarm hub supports people through cold
OL,4,Csnap health warning
OL,6,F"We encourage older people to turn
OL,7,Ftheir heating down at home and come
OL,8,Fdown to spend a few hours with us
OL,9,Fwithin the warmth of the club."
OL,11,FWith more than 30 regulars attending
OL,12,Feach week, Russell says they are
OL,13,Fcurrently managing to 'fulfil their
OL,14,Fpurpose' despite their need for
OL,15,Ffunding.
OL,17,F"We're having to ask people to go into
OL,18,Ftheir pockets, it would be good to see
OL,19,Fsome sort of funding to come back
OL,20,Fagain.
