OL,3,CWarm hub supports people through cold
OL,4,Csnap health warning
OL,6,F"The previous two years we did receive
OL,7,Ffunding through the local authority -
OL,8,Fit was really helpful and got us going.
OL,10,F"This year we have no funding at all.
OL,11,FWe managed to secure a grant from the
OL,12,FRoyal British Legion to help get us up
OL,13,Fand started. We've had to ask people
OL,14,Fto give donations if they can.
OL,16,F"It gives you a real sense of
OL,17,Fachievement when you come down here
OL,18,Fand you see the same faces coming in
OL,19,Fweek after week."
