OL,4,Csnap health warning
OL,6,FOne woman who attends the club every
OL,7,Fweek, said: "I come here because I
OL,8,Flive here on my own and I like getting
OL,9,Fout with people, it's a pleasant place
OL,10,Fto visit. You also have a nice meal
OL,11,Fand a very nice gossip to keep up with
OL,12,Feverybody."
OL,14,FAnother user said: "I just love the
OL,15,Fatmosphere, it's a nice warm space. I
OL,16,Fjust love the environment with
OL,17,Feveryone here, it's nice and friendly."
